<p>英 /blɒɡ/    美 /blɑːɡ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>写博客；写网络日志：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was encouraged to <strong>blog about</strong> the whole experience.
我被鼓励写下这次经历。</p></div>

